{
  "chapter": 15,
  "chapter_summary": "穿火红袈裟的烈火神君蔡位神出现，声称已包围蛇王，主动要求替浣花对付蛇王。萧易人喜出望外，令十年让出缺口。不料此人竟是权力帮八大天王之火王祖金殿伪装，他以烈火神功突袭十年大阵，彩衣、悲愤、燕君、白云四人瞬间殒命，十年大阵被破。祖金殿得意揭露真相：长江四棍早已被剑王杀一人、余三人被其所制。浣花剑派因此役覆没，但也因此一战名震天下。与此同时，萧秋水与宋明珠坠崖后在悬崖半腰的草虫堆上苏醒，萧秋水无意中吸食草虫汁液压制了阳极先丹的药力，宋明珠则以铁心兰花心压制了阴极先丹。萧秋水功力大增一甲子。唐朋逃出战后于天明返回找到幸存的唐方，唐方告知萧秋水可能未死的消息。铁星月与邱南顾从死人堆中爬出，虽满身伤痕但决心不顾一切前往浣花溪救援。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zu_jin_dian",
      "speaker_name": "烈火神君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“蛇王，我们已包围你了。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王少女",
      "listener": "char_zu_jin_dian",
      "text": "“朱大天王的走狗，你想怎样？”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zu_jin_dian",
      "speaker_name": "烈火神君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "text": "“这对蛇王交给我，你们继续走，不要耽误。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王老人",
      "listener": "char_zu_jin_dian",
      "text": "“你来送死，最好不过。”",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zu_jin_dian",
      "speaker_name": "烈火神君",
      "listener": "char_she_wang_lao_ren",
      "text": "“你准备死好了。”",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王少女",
      "listener": "char_zu_jin_dian",
      "text": "“你现在就死吧。”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zu_jin_dian",
      "speaker_name": "烈火神君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "text": "“你的‘十年’已被我破了。”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧易人",
      "listener": "char_zu_jin_dian",
      "text": "“你不是烈火神君？”",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zu_jin_dian",
      "speaker_name": "祖金殿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "text": "“我不是蔡位神。”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“蛇王本来就够‘蛇’，饶你聪明似鬼精，还是让蛇王给耍了。”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王老人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“其实我们跟你们那仗，早在滇池边已经打了。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zu_jin_dian",
      "speaker_name": "祖金殿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "text": "“我那一仗是为了让你信任我就是‘烈火神君’，朱大天王的人，你才会不防于我，才会让我毁了你‘十年大阵’。”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧易人",
      "listener": "char_zu_jin_dian",
      "text": "“你，究，竟，是，谁？！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zu_jin_dian",
      "speaker_name": "祖金殿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "text": "“别忘了权力帮也有个火中之王。”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧易人",
      "listener": "char_zu_jin_dian",
      "text": "“你是‘火王’祖金殿？！”",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zu_jin_dian",
      "speaker_name": "祖金殿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "text": "“正是在下。”",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zu_jin_dian",
      "speaker_name": "祖金殿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "text": "“你们萧家的人，都是角色，连萧秋水这样的武功，居然还在丹霞山逃得出我们的追杀，了不起！”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王老人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“可惜今日你却走投无路。”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_wang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "蛇王少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "“我们的人已封杀住你的退路。”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧易人",
      "listener": "char_zu_jin_dian",
      "text": "“长江四棍为何跟着你？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zu_jin_dian",
      "speaker_name": "祖金殿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "text": "“长江四棍在高要时早已被‘剑王’杀了一人，所余三人已交了给我，都已为我所制不得不跟在我，也作声不得，现在你都明白了没有？”",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧易人",
      "listener": "char_zu_jin_dian",
      "text": "“明白了。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zu_jin_dian",
      "speaker_name": "祖金殿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yi_ren",
      "text": "“那你可以死了。”",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_ming_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "宋明珠",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“你傻愕愕作什么？”",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_song_ming_zhu",
      "text": "“你不是……”",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_ming_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "宋明珠",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“草虫堆里长有一株‘铁心兰’，我采它花心吃了；草虫是至凉至阴的，铁心兰花却是至烈至刚的，我功力比你好，摔下来没晕倒，就撷来嚼食，镇住了‘阴极先丹’的药力。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_song_ming_zhu",
      "text": "“哦……”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_ming_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "宋明珠",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“你还发什么呆！我看你人很好，那种时候也不会做出……我……我很感激你……”",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_ming_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "宋明珠",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“你还不快多吸吮草虫之汁，不然那药力克不住又发作，那就……那就不好了。”",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_song_ming_zhu",
      "text": "“哦，哦……”",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_ming_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "宋明珠",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“你也不能光吃呀，要是已压制了下去……就可以停吃了……”",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_ming_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "宋明珠",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“愣子，你想点办法呀？”",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_song_ming_zhu",
      "text": "“想什么办法？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_ming_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "宋明珠",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“现在我们是上不着天，下不着地，只是山崖的中间一块小小的拗地上不上不下，你总要想个办法上去，或想个法子下去呀。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_ming_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "宋明珠",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“你是浣花剑派的人？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_song_ming_zhu",
      "text": "“我是。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_ming_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "宋明珠",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“萧易人跟你怎样称呼？”",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_song_ming_zhu",
      "text": "“他是我哥哥。”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_ming_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "宋明珠",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“你哥哥在武林中很有名气，却不料他弟弟竟那么傻呆。”",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_ming_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "宋明珠",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“怎么了？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_song_ming_zhu",
      "text": "“宋姑娘。”",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_ming_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "宋明珠",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“嗯？”",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_song_ming_zhu",
      "text": "“我是浣花萧家的人，而浣花剑派之所以有今天的急难，全系贵帮一手所赐……何况你杀劳九且伤吴财，他们都是我的好朋友……今天的事，在下是很对你不起，但到底没有毁了姑娘的名节……此后的事，咱们恩怨两分，姑娘若杀得了在下，尽杀无妨，我也没有怨怼可言……”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_ming_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "宋明珠",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“凭你的功力，也敢对我这样说话。我要杀你，易如反掌……”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_ming_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "宋明珠",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“这十余年来，除了你，没有第二个人敢对我这样说话……”",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_ming_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "宋明珠",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“要是柳五公子看见你和我共处在这里，你这一生休想有好活的了。”",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_song_ming_zhu",
      "text": "“我要有一天叫柳五知道，这纵然是个事实，但他只好认了！”",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_ming_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "宋明珠",
      "listener": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "text": "“谁说的！？”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_qiu_shui",
      "speaker_name": "萧秋水",
      "listener": "char_song_ming_zhu",
      "text": "“我，萧秋水说的。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "text": "“老铁，你还没死呀？！”",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "邱南顾",
      "listener": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "text": "“妈的兔崽子，你还想咒死我啊！”",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "text": "“有没有看见左丘？”",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "邱南顾",
      "listener": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "text": "“没有！马生根呢？”",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "text": "“也没有，他老婆……”",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "邱南顾",
      "listener": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "text": "“唐方呢？”",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "text": "“我们对不起……”",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "邱南顾",
      "listener": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "text": "“对不起老大……”",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "speaker_name": "铁星月",
      "listener": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "text": "“不管如何，我们还是要去浣花溪……纵然螳臂，也要挡车！”",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_nan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "邱南顾",
      "listener": "char_tie_xing_yue",
      "text": "“老大不在，我们更舍命也要去一趟。”",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15
    }
  ],
